<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Привязка Telegram</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
      background: #1c1c1c;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }
    .tg-link-result {
      max-width: 480px;
      width: 90%;
      padding: 32px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .tg-link-result.success {
      background: #1a3a1a;
      border: 1px solid #2d6a2d;
      color: #7ec87e;
    }
    .tg-link-result.error {
      background: #3a1a1a;
      border: 1px solid #6a2d2d;
      color: #c87e7e;
    }
    .tg-link-result a {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
      color: #a0a0a0;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <% if @success %>
    <div class="tg-link-result success">
      ✅ Telegram успешно привязан к аккаунту на форуме
      <br>
      <a href="/">← На главную</a>
    </div>
  <% else %>
    <div class="tg-link-result error">
      ❌ <%= @error_message %>
      <br>
      <a href="/">← На главную</a>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</body>
</html>
